The smartcard sub-project contains libraries and utilities for communicating
with a smartcard on a PC platform. The PCSC support libraries must be installed
prior to building this sub-project. On RedHat/CentOS systems these are the
pcsc-lite and pcsc-lite-devel packages.

OS-X includes PCSC development headers after installing "Command Line Tools,"
or by building with xcrun. Refer to Apple Technical Note TN 2339 for details:
https://developer.apple.com/library/ios/technotes/tn2339/_index.html
